  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Desktop Cate Cafe is a <strong>cute, idle management game</strong> that lives at the bottom of your screen letting you work on other tasks while your cafe runs. Design your dream cafe, unlock delicious recipes, and automate your cafe with cute cat staff! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978180/extras/5a6c7f3f7691e80a93e0fa1238084b06.poster.avif?t=1751063350\" width=800 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978180/extras/5a6c7f3f7691e80a93e0fa1238084b06.webm?t=1751063350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978180/extras/5a6c7f3f7691e80a93e0fa1238084b06.mp4?t=1751063350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Design Your Outdoor Cafe</i></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build the perfect cafe with hundreds of customization options paired with an easy to use building system that lets your creativity shine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978180/extras/1374a30cc3d8f95a443c62a58b4762a6.poster.avif?t=1751063350\" width=800 height=215 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978180/extras/1374a30cc3d8f95a443c62a58b4762a6.webm?t=1751063350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Unlock Delicious Recipes</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progress by serving customers to unlock over 150 different recipes from colorful bubble tea to mouthwatering matcha cake.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978180/extras/62166fe3eee5dd8a64ce631c783f5877.avif?t=1751063350\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978180/extras_big/62166fe3eee5dd8a64ce631c783f5877.avif?t=1751063350 width=800 height=139 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Automate with Cute Staff</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cute cat helpers will take care of the cafe while you're gone or working on other tasks! Desktop Cat cafe sits comfortably at the bottom of your screen so you can always keep your customers happy. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978180/extras/3323c2e72c5ba7b16d34e2252ca033e2.poster.avif?t=1751063350\" width=800 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978180/extras/3323c2e72c5ba7b16d34e2252ca033e2.webm?t=1751063350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Desktop Cate Cafe is a <strong>cute, idle management game</strong> that lives at the bottom of your screen letting you work on other tasks while your cafe runs. Design your dream cafe, unlock delicious recipes, and automate your cafe with cute cat staff! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978180/extras/5a6c7f3f7691e80a93e0fa1238084b06.poster.avif?t=1751063350\" width=800 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978180/extras/5a6c7f3f7691e80a93e0fa1238084b06.webm?t=1751063350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978180/extras/5a6c7f3f7691e80a93e0fa1238084b06.mp4?t=1751063350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Design Your Outdoor Cafe</i></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build the perfect cafe with hundreds of customization options paired with an easy to use building system that lets your creativity shine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978180/extras/1374a30cc3d8f95a443c62a58b4762a6.poster.avif?t=1751063350\" width=800 height=215 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978180/extras/1374a30cc3d8f95a443c62a58b4762a6.webm?t=1751063350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Unlock Delicious Recipes</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progress by serving customers to unlock over 150 different recipes from colorful bubble tea to mouthwatering matcha cake.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978180/extras/62166fe3eee5dd8a64ce631c783f5877.avif?t=1751063350\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978180/extras_big/62166fe3eee5dd8a64ce631c783f5877.avif?t=1751063350 width=800 height=139 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Automate with Cute Staff</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cute cat helpers will take care of the cafe while you're gone or working on other tasks! Desktop Cat cafe sits comfortably at the bottom of your screen so you can always keep your customers happy. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978180/extras/3323c2e72c5ba7b16d34e2252ca033e2.poster.avif?t=1751063350\" width=800 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978180/extras/3323c2e72c5ba7b16d34e2252ca033e2.webm?t=1751063350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
